@node "Future" "Future"
@{b}@{u}Future releases:@{ub}@{uu}

It is probable that DAS Software, like the classic Amiga and Amiga Power, has
no future.  We have no more graphic adventures planned.  However, I still want
to finish the Gorman Fishtank, and have plans for a one-on-one beat-em-up.
Otherwise, DAS has gasped its last.

We won't develop for the new AmigaDE.  If it doesn't run Lotus Esprit, and
doesn't contain a 68K CPU, it's not an Amiga.
@endnode

